# MoAI-ADK (Agentic Development Kit)

[English](README.md) | [í•œêµ­ì–´](README.ko.md) | [à¹„à¸—à¸¢](README.th.md) | [æ—¥æœ¬èª](README.ja.md) | [ä¸­æ–‡](README.zh.md) | [à¤¹à¤¿à¤¨à¥à¤¦à¥€](README.hi.md)

[![PyPI version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/moai-adk)](https://pypi.org/project/moai-adk/)
