| Version    | Key Features                                                                         | Date       |
| ---------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ | ---------- |
| **v0.4.11** | âœ¨ TAG Guard system + CLAUDE.md formatting improvements + Code cleanup                | 2025-10-23 |
| **v0.4.10** | ğŸ”§ Hook robustness improvements + Bilingual documentation + Template language config | 2025-10-23 |
| **v0.4.9** | ğŸ¯ Hook JSON schema validation fixes + Comprehensive tests (468/468 passing)        | 2025-10-23 |
| **v0.4.8** | ğŸš€ Release automation + PyPI deployment + Skills refinement                          | 2025-10-23 |
| **v0.4.7** | ğŸ“– Korean language optimization + SPEC-First principle documentation                 | 2025-10-22 |
| **v0.4.6** | ğŸ‰ Complete Skills v2.0 (100% Production-Ready) + 85,000 lines official docs + 300+ TDD examples | 2025-10-22 |

> ğŸ“¦ **Install Now**: `pip install moai-adk==0.4.11` or `uv tool install moai-adk==0.4.11`

